    • Constructor Detail

      • ImParameter

        public ImParameter()
        Creates a parameter set with default values.
        • primary ID = -1 (ID unknown)
        • TNCS first support = false
        • preferred language = en (English)

      • ImParameter

        public ImParameter(boolean tncsFirstSupport)
        Creates a parameter set with the TNCS first support specifically set. All other parameters have default values.
        Parameters:
        tncsFirstSupport - true if TNCS fist is supported

      • ImParameter

        public ImParameter(long primaryId,
           boolean tncsFirstSupport,
           String preferredLanguage)
        Creates a custom parameter set. The preferred language is set as Accept-Language header (RFC 3282) (e.g. Accept-Language: en).
        Parameters:
        primaryId - the primary ID
        tncsFirstSupport - true if TNCS fist is supported
        preferredLanguage - the preferred language
